{
  "doc_id": "12072",
  "text": "Our proof of (1.3), in its full generality, is based on an extension of [CITATION_1] Theorem 0.2] , where Zhang proved a Riemann-Roch type formula for certain extended versions of the Atiyah-Patodi-Singer ρ-invariant associated to the subsignature operators constructed also in [Z1] . The main method used, as in [Z1] , is the computation of the adiabatic limits of the constructed sub-signature operators, based on the techniques developed by Bismut-Cheeger [BC] and Dai [D] , as well as the local index computations developed in the papers of BismutLott [BL] and Bismut-Zhang [BZ] . Moreover, under suitable deformations of these sub-signature operators, the above arguments also lead to a new proof of (1.2). Thus, we obtain (1.4) solely in the framework of η-invariants.",
