      "span_text": "Our proof of (1.3), in its full generality, is based on an extension of Theorem 0.2], where Zhang proved a Riemann-Roch type formula for certain extended versions of the Atiyah-Patodi-Singer ρ-invariant associated to the subsignature operators constructed also in [Z1]."
